== 現況 ==
岡山神社原址現為中山公園（岡山公園）與岡山壽天宮{{r|岡}}。（石造）[[石獅子|狛犬]]1對充做（壽天宮）廟前石獅，而在公園內也保留了改為牌樓的[[鳥居|鳥居]]{{r|岡}}。其中鳥居指原岡山神社一之鳥居，戰後曾去除原鳥居的混凝土製"笠木"（上樑）並予以加工作為中山公園入口牌樓<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.google.com.tw/maps/@22.7965763,120.2931603,3a,22.3y,281.76h,90.8t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sx4wp7G8rdWqvun8zz_Vocw!2e0!7i13312!8i6656 |title = 街景中的原中山公園牌樓 |date = 2012-06 |publisher = google地圖 |language = zh-TW |accessdate = 2018-02-24 |archive-date = 2018-02-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180225064725/https://www.google.com.tw/maps/@22.7965763,120.2931603,3a,22.3y,281.76h,90.8t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sx4wp7G8rdWqvun8zz_Vocw!2e0!7i13312!8i6656 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，現已修復完成並漆成紅色。

此外在[[岡山壽天宮|岡山壽天宮]]的玉皇殿1樓內仍保留了原神社的2台神輿{{r|金1}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://sites.google.com/site/gsstktw/gsstk02/07 |title = 天照大小神轎 |publisher = 岡山壽天宮全球資訊網 |language = zh-TW |access-date = 2018-02-24 |archive-date = 2020-10-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018124338/https://sites.google.com/site/gsstktw/gsstk02/07 }}</ref>，而在金爐旁也堆置了原神社的手水缽<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://sites.google.com/site/gsstktw/gsstk02/03 |title = 岡山神社手水舍水槽 |publisher = 岡山壽天宮全球資訊網 |language = zh-TW |access-date = 2018-02-24 |archive-date = 2020-10-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018124338/https://sites.google.com/site/gsstktw/gsstk02/03 }}</ref>和石燈籠構件數枚（包含石燈籠構件"中台"、"火袋"、"寶珠"各1枚以及昭和12年（1937年）由岡山郡守飯島稔奉獻的大石燈籠（同款現存於[[高雄神社|高雄神社]]與[[嘉義神社|嘉義神社]]）構件"竿"2枚<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://sites.google.com/site/gsstktw/gsstk02/04 |title = 岡山神社石燈籠 |publisher = 岡山壽天宮全球資訊網 |language = zh-TW |access-date = 2018-02-24 |archive-date = 2020-10-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018124338/https://sites.google.com/site/gsstktw/gsstk02/04 }}</ref>）{{r|金1}}。在[[國立岡山高級農工職業學校|國立岡山高級農工職業學校]]正門右側(校園內)走道兩旁也堆置有石燈籠構件"笠"（約11枚，倒置，部分置於花盆下<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.google.com.tw/maps/@22.803311,120.2899721,3a,15y,194.21h,84t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sobdhRzvAI87hs-_9QNk1jA!2e0!7i13312!8i6656?hl=zh-TW |title = 街景中的岡山高農內的石燈籠"笠" |date = 2017-02 |publisher = google地圖 |language = zh-TW |accessdate = 2018-02-24 |archive-date = 2018-06-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180613184143/https://www.google.com.tw/maps/@22.803311,120.2899721,3a,15y,194.21h,84t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sobdhRzvAI87hs-_9QNk1jA!2e0!7i13312!8i6656?hl=zh-TW |dead-url = no }}</ref>）{{r|金1}}。而2012年時岡山公園內的中國城茶館前仍堆置有石燈籠構件"寶珠"數枚，但隨公園整建房屋拆除現已不知去向<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://blog.xuite.net/d0963064845/twblog1/123679959-2012%2F6%2F25%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E6%B4%B2%E5%B2%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%83%A1%E5%B2%A1%E5%B1%B1%E7%A5%9E%E7%A4%BE(%E4%BB%8A%E5%B2%A1%E5%B1%B1%E5%A3%BD%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%AE) |title = 高雄洲岡山郡岡山神社（今岡山壽天宮） |autho